Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”\N是基于人的渊源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是身怀六甲的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位\N是让女子借宿一宿的老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是追杀女子的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三者聚集于一家旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里日夜酒宴不断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莺声燕语觥筹交错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…儿童天真无邪的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽闻其声却不见其形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个东西\N正窥视着这名女子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其“形”正是物怪“座敷童子”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而“真”与“理”究竟是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(座敷童子)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话却说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犹记那虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却那温暖的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什么样的风景？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的下弦月隐脏在云间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述说着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又将对月长叹…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(后篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家旅馆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀有身孕的女子跟这个房间\N对不起妈妈好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有什么…\N对不起好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关联呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识那个\N被物怪杀死的男人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人…叫做直助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为何而来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了杀死我…\N跟我肚子里的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在开玩笑吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁派来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷跟夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我怀了少爷的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被允许的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋情…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷他们曾经允许我们交往
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N却又突然反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的姑娘\N不肯原谅我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太天真了\N我不在乎什么家业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也跟少爷说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想把这个孩子生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~有够烦耶你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么物怪什么妖怪来着！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这房间有物怪什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去不就没事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？走廊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…挺棘手的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别那么悠哉好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法解决啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠哉的什么也不说的\N是老板娘您吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是用来供奉祭拜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭拜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了求一点点的…安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这旅馆以前是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妓院！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这房间是做什么的老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善后用的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片墙是婴儿的坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在帮她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃我爱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是少爷…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是个下人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷跟夫人\N不会答应我们在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你嫁给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…嫁给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事\N我的心意都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只喜欢你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有件事我一定要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事你想告诉我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…肚子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经怀了少爷的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有钱\N跟谁上床你都无所谓吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼真是个愚蠢的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧德次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真~好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我也有妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人真的好温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连债都还不了的窝囊废
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么躲都是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自已都养不活真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卖来还债的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是怀了孩子怎么干活赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.39,0:14:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也怀孕了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把孩子拿掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会被座敷童子盯上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会以为可以生下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要杀我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.57,0:15:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困在这房里的物怪\N卖药的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未出生就被杀的\N那些婴儿的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只剩下“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要找出“理”就能够拔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！不要杀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些孩子有什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算\N借你腹中的胎儿到这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是\N想诞生到这世上而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让他们这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你们一起生下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算把那些物怪生下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我肚子里的\N都是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万别那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想生…我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是轻轻地抚摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够遇见你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起让你感到身体不适
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直努力熬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢你一直对我说那么多话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要你做我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择当我的孩子来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是该道谢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法当你们的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法跟你们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你不在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无法笑得开怀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能将那些无可取代的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜并活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别无所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛开在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随风缓缓飘落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不见的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子将是我此生无可比喻的珍爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.53,0:22:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了我都没吃东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的妈妈真的好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想快点跟你见面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(座敷童子  完)
